timelineItems.text: Four minutes of added time...will Robbie Keane get the goal that he's been desperate for all game?

timelineItems.desc: Attempt saved. Robbie Keane (LA Galaxy) left footed shot from the left side of the box is saved in the bottom left corner.
timelineItems.title: CROSSBAR: Robbie Keane has his shot deflected off of the woodwork

timelineItems.name: ThreeForAWin
timelineItems.text: Is it just me or have we been waiting for about 25 minutes for that 3rd goal to drop? #LAGalaxy #LAvVAN #MLS

timelineItems.comment: Attempt blocked. Gyasi Zardes (LA Galaxy) right footed shot from outside the box is blocked. Assisted by Landon Donovan.
Attempt saved. Robbie Keane (LA Galaxy) left footed shot from the left side of the box is saved in the bottom left corner. Assisted by Juninho.

timelineItems.name: LA Galaxy
timelineItems.text: OFF THE BAR FROM KEANE! #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Shawn Medow
timelineItems.text: Just not happening for Keane today #LAGalaxy

timelineItems.comment: Offside, Vancouver Whitecaps. Mauro Rosales tries a through ball, but Erik Hurtado is caught offside.
